dcterms:description: A dataset containing 1175 gallery and 300 probe shoe-print images, collected in collaboration with German State Criminal Police Offices. The probe images were digitized after being lifted with a gel foil from the ground.
dcterms:title: Footwear Impression Database (FID-300)
